#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"A delicate blend of soft pink roses and baby's breath, perfect for "
"expressing love and gratitude."
msgstr ""
"En delikat blandning av mjuka rosa rosor och baby's breath, perfekt för att "
"uttrycka kärlek och tacksamhet."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline Turner, Bouquet Designer"
msgstr "Aline Turner, bukettdesigner"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Aline is the mastermind behind our bespoke floral arrangements."
msgstr "Aline är hjärnan bakom våra skräddarsydda blomsterarrangemang."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Bloom with Joy:"
msgstr "Blomstra med glädje:"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Blushing Harmony"
msgstr "Blushing Harmony"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid ""
"Brighten any corner of the globe with our express 24-hour worldwide flower "
"delivery service."
msgstr ""
"Lys upp alla hörn av världen med vår express 24-timmarsservice för leverans "
"av blommor över hela världen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Bringing the Beauty of Nature to Your Space"
msgstr "Ta med naturens skönhet till ditt utrymme"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Celebrate with Our Best-Selling Bouquets, perfect for every occasion."
msgstr "Fira med våra bästsäljande buketter, perfekta för varje tillfälle."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Discover Our Most Loved Arrangements"
msgstr "Upptäck våra mest älskade arrangemang"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Visningsnamn"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid "Elegant Simplicity"
msgstr "Elegant enkelhet"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid ""
"Enhance your surroundings with our exquisite floral arrangements and garden "
"designs. We offer a variety of options that bring the serenity and beauty of "
"nature into your home or workspace."
msgstr ""
"Försköna din omgivning med våra utsökta blomsterarrangemang och "
"trädgårdsdesign. Vi erbjuder en mängd olika alternativ som för in naturens "
"lugn och skönhet i ditt hem eller på din arbetsplats."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_freegrid
msgid "Explore Our Gardens"
msgstr "Utforska våra trädgårdar"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_title
msgid ""
"Explore our handcrafted floral arrangements, each meticulously designed to "
"convey beauty, elegance, and a touch of nature's artistry."
msgstr ""
"Utforska våra handgjorda blomsterarrangemang, var och en noggrant utformad "
"för att förmedla skönhet, elegans och en touch av naturens konstnärskap."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_kickoff
msgid "Fresh Flowers Delivered to Your Doorstep!"
msgstr "Färska blommor levereras till din dörr!"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_image_text_overlap
msgid "Global 24-Hour Flower Delivery"
msgstr "Global blomsterförmedling dygnet runt"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_orchid.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris Joe, Customer Relations"
msgstr "Iris Joe, kundrelationer"

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
msgid "Iris ensures that each customer has a delightful experience."
msgstr "Iris ser till att varje kund får en härlig upplevelse."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_key_images
msgid ""
"Light pink blossoms with golden leaves, bringing a touch of springtime charm "
"to any space."
msgstr ""
"Ljusrosa blommor med gyllene blad som ger en touch av vårlig charm till alla "
"utrymmen."

#. module: theme_orchid
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_orchid.s_company_team_basic
